				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><table class="plainlinks ombox ombox-notice" style="">
<tr>
<td class="mbox-image"><img alt="Green check.svg" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/03/Green_check.svg/30px-Green_check.svg.png" width="30" height="30" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/03/Green_check.svg/45px-Green_check.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/03/Green_check.svg/60px-Green_check.svg.png 2x" /></td>
<td class="mbox-text" style="">This page documents an English Wikipedia <a href="Wikipedia_Policies_and_guidelines" title="Wikipedia:Policies and guidelines">policy</a>, a widely accepted standard that all editors should <a href="Wikipedia_What_%22Ignore_all_rules%22_means#Use_common_sense" title="Wikipedia:What &quot;Ignore all rules&quot; means">normally</a> follow. Changes made to it should reflect <a href="Wikipedia_Consensus" title="Wikipedia:Consensus">consensus</a>.</td>
<td class="mbox-imageright">
<table class="shortcutbox noprint" style="float: right; border: 1px solid #aaa; background: #fff; margin: 0; padding: 1px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.1em">
<tr>
<th style="border: none; background: transparent;"><span id="WP:BOTPOL"></span><small><a href="Wikipedia_Shortcut" title="Wikipedia:Shortcut">Shortcut</a>:<br />
<a href="Wikipedia_BOTPOL" title="Wikipedia:BOTPOL" class="mw-redirect">WP:BOTPOL</a></small></th>
</tr>
</table>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<table class="plainlinks ombox ombox-notice" style="">
<tr>
<td class="mbox-image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/ce/Nutshell.png" width="30" height="30" /></td>
<td class="mbox-text" style=""><b>This page in a nutshell:</b> Automated or partially automated editing processes, known as "bots", must be harmless and useful, have approval, use separate user accounts, and be operated responsibly.<br />
This wiki allows <a href="http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/bot_policy#Global_bots" class="extiw" title="m:bot policy">global bots</a> subject to <a href="Wikipedia_Global_rights_usage#Global_bots" title="Wikipedia:Global rights usage" class="mw-redirect">local requirements</a>.</td>
</tr>
</table>
<table class="plainlinks ombox ombox-notice hlist" style="">
<tr>
<td class="mbox-empty-cell"></td>
<td class="mbox-text" style="text-align: center;">
<div>
<ul>
<li><a href="Wikipedia_Bots" title="Wikipedia:Bots"><b>Overview of bots</b></a></li>
